    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been fully overhauled for optimal phase timing. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring maximum traction. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout, maintaining factory-spec torsional rigidity. Finished in Carbon Black with a flawless Nappa leather interior, this vehicle exhibits zero mechanical deflection and a comprehensive service dossier. A rare, collector-tier example for the discerning enthusiast.",
